description: Recently noted as Houston's Top Ten Restaurants to Try in CultureMap Houston http://houston.culturemap.com/news/restaurants-bars/06-02-15-where-to-eat-right-now-10-distinctive-new-restaurants-that-are-definitely-worth-a-try-in-june/Bonjour Creperie hails from Europe to Houston! Allow us to spread love to your event. Serving a wide assortment of sweet and savory crepes that are gluten free! We have catered at many of Houston's hottest events including the Houston Polo Club, Charity Golf Events, River Oaks charity gala, Neiman Marcus and Dress for Success spring event. We have also worked with many publications such as the Houstonia. We are very affordable, delicious and fresh. Welcome us to your event and allow us to spread the good food of the world!
name: Bonjour Creperie (Houston)
